I didn't have room to try their boba tea or pho, maybe next time.
Service was quick and friendly.
The prices for sandwiches are definitely a great deal.
I think I'd definitely get Hue Thai's sandwich to a Subway 7 out of 10 times.
I'll have to try Lee's Sandwiches or other Vietnamese restaurants to compare, but I thought getting take-out at Hue Thai was pretty good.

